author: prbuzz.com
title: Come See SynQor at DSEI, Sept 2015!
text:
Boxborough, MA – September 8, 2015 – SynQor, Inc. is exhibiting at the Defence & Security Equipment International Exhibition (DSEI) in London, UK. DSEI will be held Sept 15th-18th at ExCel Royal Victoria Dock, 1 Western Gateway, London E16 1XL.
SynQor brings field proven high-efficiency synchronous-rectifier technology to the Military/Aerospace industry with its MilQor® series of Hi-Rel and Mil-COTS DC-DC & AC-DC converters and filters, as well as our Military-Grade UPS and Power Systems. All products are DSEIgned and manufactured in the USA, with world-class performance and flexible factory scheduling.
Visit SynQor in Stand # S9-200 to learn more about our industry-leading technologies.
For more information email SynQor at or contact your local representative.
About SynQor: Located in Boxborough, MA USA, SynQor is a leading supplier of power conversion solutions to the military, avionics, transportation, medical, industrial, telecommunications and computing markets. SynQor's innovative products are DSEIgned to exceed the demanding performance, quality, and reliability requirements of today's power electronic engineers who develop leading-edge infrastructure hardware. SynQor provides all the power conversion modules needed to build a power system, and it also provides complete power systems. SynQor's capabilities include both standard and custom solutions, and it delivers them with industry leading service and support. SynQor's total commitment to quality, customer satisfaction and continuous improvement drives our business processes.
